<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Exercise Tracker</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Noto+Sans:400,700" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Exercise Tracker</h1>
      <div>This is the fourth project in Apis and Microservices section from updated <a href="https://learn.freecodecamp.org/apis-and-microservices/apis-and-microservices-projects/exercise-tracker">freeCodeCamp</a> curriculum.</div>

      <p><i>There are no specific user stories, except functional similarity with <a href="https://fuschia-custard.glitch.me/">provided example</a>.</i></p>

      <h3>Create a new user</h3>
      <form class="create-user" method="post">
        <div>
          <label for="username">Name:</label>
          <input type="text" id="username" name="name">
        </div>
        <button>Submit</button>
      </form>

      <h3>Add an exercise</h3>
      <form class="add-exercise" method="post">
        <div>
          <label for="user-id">UserID:</label>
          <input type="text" id="user-id" name="id">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="description">Description:</label>
          <input type="text" id="description" name="description">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="duration">Duration:</label>
          <input type="text" id="duration" placeholder="mins." name="duration">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="date">Date:</label>
          <input type="text" id="date" placeholder="yyyy-mm-dd" name="date">
        </div>
        <button>Submit</button>
      </form>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>
